<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; padding:4pt; line-height:1.25em; text-align:center; font-size:8pt;"><a href="/wiki/File:Slotin_Los_Alamos.jpg" class="image" title="Slotin Los Alamos.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/42/Slotin_Los_Alamos.jpg/225px-Slotin_Los_Alamos.jpg" width="225" height="277" border="0" /></a><br />
